28:43.256 --> 28:44.690
Hank, have you been
working out?

28:44.691 --> 28:47.259
- Uh, a little, but...
- Oh, my goodness.

28:47.260 --> 28:48.560
These are amazing.

28:48.561 --> 28:50.129
